​This structure is derived from ManufacturedItemDefinition

Summary

Mandatory: 3 elements (5 nested mandatory elements)
Prohibited: 1 element

Structures

This structure refers to these other structures:

  • Organization (ePI) (http://hl7.eu/fhir/ig/gravitate-health/StructureDefinition/Organization-uv-epi)

Slices

This structure defines the following Slices:

  • The element ManufacturedItemDefinition.manufacturedDoseForm.coding is sliced based on the value of value:system
  • The element ManufacturedItemDefinition.unitOfPresentation.coding is sliced based on the value of value:system
  • The element ManufacturedItemDefinition.property is sliced based on the value of value:type
  • The element ManufacturedItemDefinition.property.value[x] is sliced based on the value of type:$this
